$OpenBSD$

+-----------------------------------------------------------------------
| Running ${FULLPKGNAME} on OpenBSD
+-----------------------------------------------------------------------

To run yquake2 on OpenBSD, you need the original The Reckoning data files.

Copy *.pak and the video directory to ${TRUEPREFIX}/share/yquake2/xatrix/
and start up yquake2.

quake2 +set game xatrix
